  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE:</strong> Deadly Land is currently undergoing a massive overhaul. The \"<strong>Rebirth Update</strong>\" (2.0) described below is in active development and represents the future of the game. By purchasing now, you directly support a solo developer in completing this vision. You will get immediate access to the <strong>Classic Version</strong>, and the 2.0 update will be delivered automatically and for free as soon as it is ready.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >☢️ THE REBIRTH UPDATE: A NEW ERA BEGINS (COMING SOON) ☢️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deadly Land</strong> is being reborn! While you can play the current version today, I am working hard behind the scenes on the biggest transformation in the game's history. The <strong>Rebirth Update (2.0)</strong> will be free for all current and future owners.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/0506cd52da66f403fe15c6f110ba336b.poster.avif?t=1770134832\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/0506cd52da66f403fe15c6f110ba336b.webm?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/0506cd52da66f403fe15c6f110ba336b.mp4?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br><strong>What’s coming in Deadly Land 2.0? </strong> <br>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Loadout System:</strong> Define your playstyle. Customize weapons with attachments, extended magazines, and unique skins.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/1dc0ad4f1c26fa34ff909b6a1976263a.poster.avif?t=1770134832\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/1dc0ad4f1c26fa34ff909b6a1976263a.webm?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/1dc0ad4f1c26fa34ff909b6a1976263a.mp4?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Massive Visual Overhaul:</strong> Experience a more immersive world with dynamic weather, improved lighting, and brand-new 3D models. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat Refined:</strong> With completely overhauled animations, both gunplay and melee combat feel more fluid and impactful than ever.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/659a90e1416e5a8dba5b127094b0b98b.poster.avif?t=1770134832\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/659a90e1416e5a8dba5b127094b0b98b.webm?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/659a90e1416e5a8dba5b127094b0b98b.mp4?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Map & Secrets:</strong> Explore a more detailed world with deadlier threats and hidden rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Support the development now by grabbing the Classic version today and be ready for the day everything changes!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🕹️ CURRENT STATE: THE CLASSIC VERSION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deadly Land</strong> is a <strong>fast-paced First Person Zombie Shooter</strong>. Team up with up to 3 other players and survive against increasingly powerful waves of the undead.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiplayer | Co-op | Up to 4 Players | Lobby</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/b70a2a09d192428b74b6c94c700bb134.poster.avif?t=1770134832\" width=634 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/b70a2a09d192428b74b6c94c700bb134.webm?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces in 4-player lobbies and choose your character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Different Weapons with different Extensions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/b5f17e4cfd30bf8027db40de0b76bc49.poster.avif?t=1770134832\" width=626 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/b5f17e4cfd30bf8027db40de0b76bc49.webm?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/b5f17e4cfd30bf8027db40de0b76bc49.mp4?t=1770134832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons differ in fire rate, range, damage, penetration, and recoil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Black-Market Dealer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/7a7b4a7b04f39226ea6389009dbdca9a.avif?t=1770134832\" width=626 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find him hidden in the shadows to buy gear and upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Boss Fight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/bc942b429c11614c691d22fcfd5c4393.avif?t=1770134832\" width=626 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every Boss has unique mechanics and enhanced attributes. You'll need a strategy to survive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character & Weapon Boosts</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234260/extras/d10b1074579871d6b5ee59a43c0d1a87.avif?t=1770134832\" width=626 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use vending machines to enhance your health regeneration or weapon skills (e.g., magazine size).</p>",
